messages.message: Who would be the current owner of Mohamed’s code for person name detection in the custom udfs package? We are wondering if it is safe to comment out/remove since it is now available as a refiner capability
by remove, we mean “comment it out” so that (a) we know it’s not being used and (b) it doesn’t break CI (the code isn’t PY3-compatible).
Although remove may also be a good idea, because the logic has been transferred to a new module, so there is no loss of code by removing this version (i believe)

you can chat with me about it — and i’d like to loop in @Kerry and @Balaram about the functionality in the future — they will be able to tell you whether there is any loss of functionality or anything
